flowchart LR
  Human["Human operator"]
  Matrix["Matrix Homeserver<br/>collaboration and projections"]
  Gateway["Matrix AppService Gateway<br/>auth, validation, idempotency"]
  Runtime["TypeScript Runtime<br/>source of truth for task orchestration"]
  Store[("Task Store<br/>runtime state")]
  ObjectStore[("Object Store<br/>logs and artifacts")]
  GitHub["GitHub<br/>PRs, checks, comments"]
  Codex["Codex Worker<br/>scoped execution"]
  MemoryReview["Human memory review<br/>proposal only"]

  Human -->|"intent, approval decision"| Matrix
  Matrix -->|"untrusted events"| Gateway
  Gateway -->|"validated runtime commands"| Runtime
  Runtime -->|"status, proof summary, approval request"| Gateway
  Gateway -->|"projection events"| Matrix

  Runtime <--> Store
  Runtime -->|"work cell launch"| Codex
  Codex -->|"result, artifact refs"| Runtime
  Codex -->|"logs, diffs, outputs"| ObjectStore
  Runtime -->|"proof refs"| ObjectStore
  Runtime -->|"approved PR action"| GitHub
  Runtime -->|"memory proposal"| MemoryReview

  Matrix -. no runtime state .-> Store
  Matrix -. no raw proof logs .-> ObjectStore
